nodes.text: Case file 127456 was part of the Galactic Republic's official records and was related to the disappearance of Jedi Master Sifo-Dyas. It had been sealed by the Office of the Chancellor, so when Grand Master Yoda was looking for information on Sifo-Dyas after his lightsaber was found on the Oba Diah moon, Yoda went to Supreme Chancellor Palpatine to ask about the file. Palpatine claimed that the records had been sealed during the tenure of his predecessor, Finis Valorum.
